<h2><a name="explicit" id="explicit">explicit</a></h2>
<div class="level2">

<p>
When a constructor is specified as explicit, no automatic conversion will be
used with that constructor â€“ but parameters passed to the constructor may
still be converted. For example:
</p>
<pre class="c code c++" style="font-family:monospace;">    <span class="kw4">struct</span> foo <span class="br0">&#123;</span>
      explicit foo<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">int</span> a <span class="br0">&#41;</span>
        <span class="sy0">:</span> a_<span class="br0">&#40;</span> a <span class="br0">&#41;</span>
      <span class="br0">&#123;</span> <span class="br0">&#125;</span>
&nbsp;
      <span class="kw4">int</span> a_;
    <span class="br0">&#125;</span>;
&nbsp;
    <span class="kw4">int</span> bar<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="kw4">const</span> foo <span class="sy0">&amp;</span> f <span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#123;</span>
      <span class="kw1">return</span> f.<span class="me1">a_</span>;
    <span class="br0">&#125;</span>
&nbsp;
    bar<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="nu0">1</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;  <span class="co1">// fails because an implicit conversion from int to foo</span>
               <span class="co1">// is forbidden by explicit.</span>
&nbsp;
    bar<span class="br0">&#40;</span> foo<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="nu0">1</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;  <span class="co1">// works -- explicit call to explicit constructor.</span>
&nbsp;
    bar<span class="br0">&#40;</span> static_cast<span class="sy0">&lt;</span>foo<span class="sy0">&gt;</span><span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="nu0">1</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;  <span class="co1">// works -- call to explicit constructor via explicit cast.</span>
&nbsp;
    bar<span class="br0">&#40;</span> foo<span class="br0">&#40;</span> <span class="nu16">1.0</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span> <span class="br0">&#41;</span>;  <span class="co1">// works -- explicit call to explicit constructor</span>
                        <span class="co1">// with automatic conversion from float to int.</span></pre>
</div>
